{"tid":1537433,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【反送中原創】【MV】《致義士》","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T13:30:34.000Z","uid":196604,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0218d553bd4c97262a79160f887cf096f888c1bb","tid":1537433,"uid":196604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"在短短數個月裡，我們都失去了身邊的那位，那位曾經共同進退的戰友。<br />\n我們不會忘記。你們所付託的，會傳承下去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fIpRoDyLaws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfIpRoDyLaws&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3J1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=715b4827\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fIpRoDyLaws</a><br />\n<br />\n《致義士》<br />\n<br />\n在那天 又再翻播千遍<br />\n是你交出那份信念<br />\n磷火漆黑一閃 無悔於這擱淺<br />\n<br />\n靜默這分鐘昐相見 念記心中繫着一線<br />\n事過境遷再變 寒冬不可摧毀那奉獻<br />\n<br />\n連夜徹晚沾上血汗 抵抗硝煙荊棘之創<br />\n狼藉遍野以初心穿街過巷<br />\n<br />\n如若你已靠緊天國 給吹奏喚應心靈號角<br />\n可否靠着聲音 安置這付託"},{"pid":"4e53a640b81c6a6ffdf33f0ed7061aebd1b80b1e","tid":1537433,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"658e9684e093af1d7883b62d38b9e0fefafee55b","tid":1537433,"uid":111982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:24:24.000Z","msg":"【Google 廣告】上線啦 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535377</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請多多關注 比下意見"},{"pid":"343fc1c7025e2d3be1f33f91590c49f67f9303d6","tid":1537433,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪、減少淘寶<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少碰中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.04"},{"pid":"65ec4976b68f11b6b3a460a235ee24a6ef68763f","tid":1537433,"uid":196604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e53a640b81c6a6ffdf33f0ed7061aebd1b80b1e","tid":1537433,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />